      "text": "Keep Parallel Threads Separate\nYou can run multiple threads at once, but avoid\nhaving two threads modify the same files.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-75f30af4fda2",
      "originalText": "Keep Parallel Threads Separate\nYou can run multiple threads at once, but avoid having two threads modify the same files.",
